data.title: Sharks in the Mediterranean: On The Trail of Great White Sharks - Watch Movies & TV Shows
data.meta_description: "It grabbed Jack Smedley and had no intention of ever letting him go." The words of British Fisheries scientist, Ian Fergusson, on one of 18 fatal attacks by sharks in the Med. Together with Fergusson's research, eye-witness accounts and reconstructions of shark attacks, Equinox proves the existence of a great white shark community in the Mediterranean... and their meal of choice.
